txt.en: 'Do you think you are ready for a true challenge adventurer? Gortheron the Doom-caller, most powerful and leader of the Gaunt-lords, has come to Enedwaith. He stands now in his fortress, Ost Dunhoth, and plots to claim all of Middle-earth for his Dark Lord.\n\n'I do not know if he can be stopped, but we must do what we can to slow him. I ask that you venture to Ost Dunhoth and slay as many of its denizens as you may. Gortheron is a threat we cannot ignore.'
'It may only be a small victory, and short-lived, as no doubt those forces will be replaced, but we can rest easy today knowing it was a victory.'
'If we are to survive these dark times, we must strike where we can.'
Ost Dunhoth is the fortress of Gortheron the Doom-caller.
Ost Dunhoth is in southern Enedwaith.\n\nYou have been asked to venture to Ost Dunhoth and defeat many of its denizens.
Return to the Rangers of Thrór's Coomb
The Rangers in Thrór's Coomb will be pleased to hear you have culled some of Gortheron's forces.
